        {
            "name": "Saurian Warmonger",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "These saurians adopt warfare as their primary role and greatest calling. They particularly excel at taking slaves.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 37",
